K9Styles_backgroundColorChooseAccountHeader

public static final int K9Styles_backgroundColorChooseAccountHeader

This symbol is the offset where the R.attr.backgroundColorChooseAccountHeader attribute's value can be found in the K9Styles array.

Must be a color value, in the form of "#rgb", "#argb", "#rrggbb", or "#aarrggbb".

This may also be a reference to a resource (in the form "@[package:]type:name") or theme attribute (in the form "?[package:][type:]name") containing a value of this type.
